	<description>	
		Dangers Afloat is a digital board game about distrust and betrayal on the high seas.
Play with your friends as a crew of rowdy pirates, and work together to guide the boat through stormy seas and get your hands on the Legendary Pirate Treasure!
But be careful! For there is a traitor in the crew.
So if you want to reach the treasure, communication is your most reliable weapon.
	</description>
		
